# CLAUDE.md — Weather Dashboard API

## Project Overview
<!-- Fill this in -->
This is a REST API that serves weather data, built with Express and TypeScript.

## Key Commands
- `npm run dev` — Start dev server with hot reload
- `npm run test` — Run tests with Vitest
- `npm run lint` — Type-check with TypeScript

## Coding Standards
- Use TypeScript strict mode — no `any` types
- Use Express Router for route organization
- Use interfaces for all request/response shapes
