## API Conventions
- All endpoints return JSON
- Error responses use format: `{ error: string, status: number }`
- Success responses use format: `{ data: T }`

## Testing Requirements
- Use Vitest for all tests
- Test files: `*.test.ts` next to source files
- Test the service layer (business logic), not Express routes directly

## Do NOT
- Use `any` type
- Make real HTTP calls to external APIs (use mock data)
- Skip error handling on route handlers
